org.itsnat.comp.button.normal
Interface ItsNatHTMLInputImage

All Superinterfaces:
ItsNatButton, ItsNatButtonNormal, ItsNatComponent, ItsNatElementComponent, ItsNatHTMLElementComponent, ItsNatHTMLFormComponent, ItsNatHTMLInput, ItsNatHTMLInputButtonNormal, ItsNatUserData
public interface ItsNatHTMLInputImage
extends ItsNatHTMLInputButtonNormal

Is the interface of HTML <input> based components with "image" attribute. This component type works as a normal button.

ItsNat provides a default implementation of this interface.
